message.body: Just saw news about collapsed building in philly. Just checking to be sure you and kennedy are ok. Please let us know. Thanks aunt karla
We are fine, thanks for checking. Awful though, it was an apartment and a store.
Thanks for letting me know. Hope you guys are doing good. When are you coming home?
We're doin well. How are the Burtons? I'm planning on August 19th - 23rd
We are keeping busy. See you soon.
